                <head>45. Telegram 356 from Geneva<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d45fn1">Source:
                        Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/8–855. Confidential;
                        Priority.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Geneva</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1955-08-08"
                            >August 8, 1955, 9 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d45-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d45-1"/>
                <p>356. From <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName>.</p>
                <p>Denny article August 4 referred to Deptel 400 not available here.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GFC_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Gowen</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
